ygData.messageBody:
Well, That must be so. Ogre SK here, 160 str, level 29, hitting for 63 max with the Dark Reaver.

----- Original Message -----
From: Joey
To: shadowknight@onelist.com
Sent: Tuesday, October 26, 1999 6:56 PM
Subject: Re: [shadowknight] Big races


Actually, I am a 33rd level DE sk, and with my reaver I do between 55 and 60 max, my strength with the sword buff is only around 125 or so, now I was grouping with a troll SK the other day, and her strength was near 200, and she was whacking for about 80 points max, now while this is a hug diffeerence in strength, it does show that it does count.

Tesaar Grimm
Hand of Innoruuk
The Rathe

"
